Liono: ::Picks up Plissanta come signal:: Tigerhawk your in charge. 
SilverBolt set up the defense grid and make sure all the maximals are in the 
base. ::Goes into docking bay:: ::comlink:: Plissanta I'm coming hang in 
there.   

Tigerhawk: Good luck. Its time Liono You and I both Know it. You have to take 
it out its your gift from the matrix.

Liono: ::Removes the 7 Foot sword From the black case:: The Dragon Slayer the 
sword use to end the great war the Sword that killed Galvatron. I guess I'm 
ready my     father Hot Rod gave me this. 

Tigerhawk: you have a fembot in distress to rescue after all Phoenix is in 
the claw and something tell me he is not going to leave.

Liono: ::Sword Rotates once and attaches its self to Liono's back:: Your 
right ::pulls the cover off  a Hovercycle and lets the engine Roar:: I'm 
coming ::hitting the gas and Flies out the maximal docking bay racing off the 
edge of the Island spreading his wings gliding towards the location 
Plissanta::
